summary: The Culture section offers a curated selection of resources focused on enriching your personal and professional ecosystem. Currently, it features the course 'Cultivate Your Ecosystem,' which guides you through discovering personal strengths, weaknesses, performing a SWOT analysis of your startup, and formulating critical asks. This approach is essential for self-awareness, strategic planning, and effective networking.
excerpt: Explore the 'Cultivate Your Ecosystem' course: a comprehensive guide to self-awareness, strategic planning, and effective networking for personal and professional growth.
